{"tid":1516600,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［召集所有藝術細胞］ 革命Logo","createTime":"2019-08-29T15:22:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T15:52:11.000Z","uid":280249,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e957a4b9e96117746f7c5418388f4308f468abc1","tid":1516600,"uid":280249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:22:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">革命Logo的重要性</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">展示聲勢、凝聚盟友</span> <br />\n睇一個人望住個Logo既眼神，應該會分得出佢係自己友定敵人（肅然起敬/堅定vs 不恥/恥笑）<br />\n好似Hunger Games咁，學舌鳥Logo<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">Logo必須符合以下條件</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. 簡單、易畫</span> <br />\n-我地兩三筆畫完，但可能對家要花一段時間先擦得甩<br />\n-唔可以太難，要個個都識畫<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2. 具代表性</span><br />\n-要比人知道我地係邊個<br />\n-唔可以比人誤以為係對家的Logo<br />\n-要所有人一睇就知道係講緊呢場革命<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">3. 要有意思</span><br />\n-唔可以9畫<br />\n-要比人知道我地爭取緊啲咩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">跪求各位藝術巴絲一齊諗諗佢，希望不久既將來可以見到一街都係</span></span>"},{"pid":"c9d4b28b4faf66d315d018271b8c8268df9e40ea","tid":1516600,"uid":280249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:23:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07c8733fd100727df83e121f0de9d46284313aae","tid":1516600,"uid":231818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:23:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bqBOnuf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbqBOnuf.jpg&h=a519857e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n環球時報總編輯胡錫進尼左香港<br />\n佢話會去示威現場<br />\n同青年對話<br />\n佢對話完<br />\n係大陸人眼中實更有權威<br />\n到時輸出革命會更難<br />\n<br />\n建議大家係佢落場時<br />\n準備定中共啲衰野<br />\n同一定要影住佢<br />\n錄低佢up過啲咩"},{"pid":"f498a0491af57420381b4e332ee48dd885c1f43c","tid":1516600,"uid":280249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:24:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebd73a1d9bb6f7eb76d715305200157d90093358","tid":1516600,"uid":280249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:25:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1de4f2eab101c9245b4a9c5c177f2d4693ae46a","tid":1516600,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:25:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-kSKnsJtQSEg/Wli6ea4eQRI/AAAAAAAACZY/Li6ZPRpQG4g28fvOcS3SHLugHY5_o5CiQCLcBGAs/s1600/0%2B%25281%2529.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-kSKnsJtQSEg%2FWli6ea4eQRI%2FAAAAAAAACZY%2FLi6ZPRpQG4g28fvOcS3SHLugHY5_o5CiQCLcBGAs%2Fs1600%2F0%252B%2525281%252529.jpg&h=20e45b8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n例子"},{"pid":"d47240af318bc2cdd60399b52f185b7bdfc907ee","tid":1516600,"uid":280249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:25:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b245d66abbbf46da2a08fc32a960304bc6b904bf","tid":1516600,"uid":280249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:29:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a65dc0b1979160f3e8cdd658dd71afdb16731f61","tid":1516600,"uid":280249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:30:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dfaab6fef54d7482bed89ff46e4d04f537b2a78","tid":1516600,"uid":280249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:30:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ebbdd0edd8c67fc4ac70b0f94c8c9af7ae00fd1","tid":1516600,"